data.description: Introducing an exquisite, custom-crafted home spanning 3,387 sq. ft. This masterpiece showcases meticulous attention to detail across its 4 bedrooms, with a luxurious master suite conveniently located on the lower level. The master suite boasts a steam room and spa tub, offering the pinnacle of relaxation. A spacious office, adorned with high ceilings, sets the tone for productivity and elegance. Step into the gorgeous family room, complete with a fireplace that exudes warmth and charm. The open kitchen floor plan, along with a formal dining room and breakfast bar, provides a seamless flow, ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. Beyond aesthetics, this home's functionality shines with a great laundry room and a loft that adds versatility to the layout. Ascend to the balcony, where stunning views await, creating a serene retreat.
